==English==

===Noun===
'''[[present]] [[continuous]]'''

# {{grammar}} A [[tense]] that describes an [[action]] carried out for an [[indefinite]] [[period]] of time in the present. In English it is formed by use of [[am]] with a [[present participle]].
#*Example: "I am editing this dictionary."

==Usage notes==
If there is a condition that would stop the action it is stated after (thus making it the same as the present unmodified verb)
#*Example: "I'm playing Resident Evil until dinner is ready".

